# How to use GitHub to visualise your work
The GOV.UK Design System uses GitHub Projects to manage the team's workflow. This tool allows the team to work in the open and encourages contribution from users to the code base and guidance. 

This guide will include a series of videos explaining how to complete various tasks on GitHub to ensure the your work is visualised.

